metadata.name: MEDEA
metadata.description:
Medea, the story of whom is based on her anger, is fascinating us with her bright-coloured eyes. Medea stands for the solid appearance of matriarchy. Properly speaking, she represents a substantial figure of a women who could endure plenty of hardships for her loved ones. Indeed, she is a sheer example of a person who can risk anything for them. On the other hand, Medea is an example manipulated and described adversely not only because she has a solid stance but she has a voice in a patriarchal society, as well. A woman respected for both her hatred and power, Medea.

Size : 3200x4000
Format : .PNG
